OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772679804
OL,3,CBBC to publish response to
OL,4,CGovernment's consultation on its future
OL,6,FThe BBC's fixed-term charter should be
OL,7,Fbrought to an end, the corporation is
OL,8,Fexpected to say later when it
OL,9,Fpublishes its response to a Government
OL,10,Fconsultation on its own future.
OL,12,FThe Press Association understands that
OL,13,Fas part of the Charter Review, the BBC
OL,14,Fwants to end the way previous reviews
OL,15,Fhave lasted for a defined period of
OL,16,Ftime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
