PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772679804
OL,3,CBBC to publish response to
OL,4,CGovernment's consultation on its future
OL,6,FThe corporation is due to publish its
OL,7,Fresponse to the Government's
OL,8,Fconsultation on its future at midday
OL,9,Fon Thursday as it looks, according to
OL,10,Fone source, to reassert its
OL,11,F"editorial, creative and operational
OL,12,Findependence".
OL,14,FThe charter sets out the BBC's public
OL,15,Fpurpose and is the constitutional
OL,16,Fbasis for the corporation, which is
OL,17,Fpredominantly funded through the
OL,18,Flicence fee, paid for by UK TV-
OL,19,Fwatching households.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772679804
OL,3,CBBC to publish response to
OL,4,CGovernment's consultation on its future
OL,6,FRenewed around every 10 years, its
OL,7,Fcurrent charter ends in December 2027.
OL,9,FBut as part of its own response to a
OL,10,FGovernment consultation, the BBC is
OL,11,Fexpected to float the idea of ending
OL,12,Fthe expiry date, and with it the
OL,13,Frecurring threat to its existence.
OL,15,FIt is also thought to be proposing
OL,16,Fchanges to the way that board
OL,17,Fappointments are made so that they
OL,18,Ffollow a new and more clearly defined
OL,19,Fprocess.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772679804
OL,3,CBBC to publish response to
OL,4,CGovernment's consultation on its future
OL,6,FBosses at the corporation are also
OL,7,Funderstood to be looking at ways of
OL,8,Fensuring its audiences are brought
OL,9,Finto the decision-making process, as
OL,10,Fwell as improving its complaints
OL,11,Fprocess.
OL,13,FThe BBC's response to the Government's
OL,14,FCharter Review Green Paper on its
OL,15,Ffuture is also expected to see the
OL,16,Fcorporation make the case for two
OL,17,Fother key areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772679804
OL,3,CBBC to publish response to
OL,4,CGovernment's consultation on its future
OL,6,FOne is thought to be ensuring a
OL,7,Funiversal funding model fit for the
OL,8,Ffuture in order to support universal
OL,9,Fpublic service media.
OL,11,FAnd secondly, modernising regulation
OL,12,Fto enable the BBC to keep pace with
OL,13,Fglobal competition and rapid
OL,14,Ftechnological change.
OL,16,FA BBC source said: "When it comes to
OL,17,Findependence, perceptions matter as
OL,18,Fmuch as reality, and the audience has
OL,19,Fspoken.
OL,26,@xD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772679804
OL,3,CBBC to publish response to
OL,4,CGovernment's consultation on its future
OL,6,F"This charter must find ways to
OL,7,Freassert the BBC's editorial, creative
OL,8,Fand operational independence, so the
OL,9,FBBC can continue to be a universally
OL,10,Fsupported, trusted, unifying force.
OL,12,F"At the same time, we want to keep
OL,13,Fmodernising the BBC and find new ways
OL,14,Fto open up our thinking, plans and
OL,15,Fdecision making to our audience, so
OL,16,Fthey are more involved and play a
OL,17,Fgreater role in the BBC of the future."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772679804
OL,3,CBBC to publish response to
OL,4,CGovernment's consultation on its future
OL,6,FThe Government launched its Charter
OL,7,FReview Green Paper in December, and
OL,8,Fsaid it will look at reforming the
OL,9,Flicence fee and consider more
OL,10,Fcommercial revenue options for the BBC.
OL,12,FSpeaking at the time, outgoing
OL,13,Fdirector-general Tim Davie urged
OL,14,Feveryone "who cares about the success
OL,15,Fof the UK's world-leading creative
OL,16,Findustries to have their say".
OL,18,F"At the BBC, we want change, so we can
OL,19,Fcontinue to deliver for the UK for
OL,20,Fgenerations to come," he added.
OL,26,@vD@JOUxD@]O]zD@AOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772679804
OL,3,CBBC to publish response to
OL,4,CGovernment's consultation on its future
OL,6,F"We want to secure a public service
OL,7,FBBC that is independent, sustainably
OL,8,Ffunded for the long term, and meets
OL,9,Four audience's needs."
OL,11,FMr Davie resigned as director-general
OL,12,Fin November following allegations that
OL,13,Fthe BBC selectively edited a speech by
OL,14,FDonald Trump on the day of the US
OL,15,FCapitol attack for a Panorama
OL,16,Fdocumentary.
OL,18,FRhodri Talfan Davies has been
OL,19,Fconfirmed as the corporation's interim
OL,20,Fdirector-general and will take on the
OL,21,Frole from April 3.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@VO]
